    <sec id="SEC2-4">
      <title>Construction of 3D virtual cells</title>
      <p>We demonstrate iSMODâs 3D reconstruction annotation and data integration capabilities through the four virtual cells shown in Figure <xref rid="F4" ref-type="fig">4B</xref> andÂ <xref rid="F4" ref-type="fig">E</xref>â<xref rid="F4" ref-type="fig">G</xref>, which have been visualized in an interactive manner on the homepage GUI of iSMOD. Specifically, the construction of virtual cells can be described in two steps: 3D data collection and 3D modeling.</p>
